	<text>
		<body xml:lang="en">
			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_002138_0001"/><!--pb/@n='11r'-->
<!--headed notepaper--><!--
<p rend="right"><placeName>Newstead Abbey</placeName> <lb/></p>
<p rend="right"><placeName>Mansfield</placeName> <lb/><placeName> Notts</placeName> <lb/></p>-->
<lb/><p rend="right">12 Dec <hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> 1864</p>
<lb/><p>My Dear <persName>Kirk</persName>
<lb/>You are to come 
<lb/>at any time before 
<lb/>the 28 or 29<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi> that 
<lb/>you like and stay 
<lb/>a month if you 
<lb/>can - for I was 
<lb/>asked if you 
<lb/>could not come 
<lb/>before the time 
<lb/>I mentioned and 
<lb/><gap extent="1" unit="words" agent="damage"/>

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_002138_0002"/><!--pb/@n='11v'-->
<lb/>I could not answer 
<lb/>I was told to say 
<lb/>as above - I hear 
<lb/>the shooting going 
<lb/>on just now<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p>I enclose a 
<lb/>cheque for £10 
<lb/>which you will 
<lb/>be good enough 
<lb/>to bring in gold 
<lb/>when you come<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>Say to the cashier 
<lb/>that I had this 
<lb/>cheque book with 
<lb/>me in Africa and 

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_002138_0003"/><!--pb/@n='12r'-->
<lb/>don<reg>'</reg>t know if 
<lb/>any alteration is 
<lb/>required as to 
<lb/>stamps<reg>.</reg>
<lb/><addSpan spanTo="#p12r-01" place="marginleft"><!--addSpan/@place='left margin of fol. 12r'--></addSpan>And pay for yourself out of £10<reg>.</reg><anchor xml:id="p12r-01"/></p>
<lb/><p>Bring please a 
<lb/>black doll, dressed, 
<lb/>for one of the little 
<lb/>girls for 4 or 5 shillings<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>One has a black 
<lb/>doll &amp; I wish to give 
<lb/>one to the other - <persName>Sir
<lb/><add place="marginleft">Admiral</add> George Lambert</persName>
<lb/>is here &amp; so is <persName>
<lb/>David Kennedy</persName> a 
<lb/>great Indian hunter 
<lb/>but very modest 
<lb/>civil fellow 

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_002138_0004"/><!--pb/@n='12v'-->
<lb/><!-- check foliation, this was listed as 13v -->and if you don<reg>'</reg>t mind 
<lb/>burdening yourself 
<lb/>buy a couple of 
<lb/><placeName>Shetland</placeName><choice><sic>woolen</sic><corr>woollen</corr></choice>
<lb/>drawers - the <placeName>Shetland</placeName>
<lb/>shop nearly opposite 
<lb/>the school of geology 
<lb/><placeName>Jermyn St</placeName> - White 
<lb/>soft thick <choice><sic>woolen</sic><corr>woollen</corr></choice> is 
<lb/>the kind. Are you 
<lb/>up in fish culture. We 
<lb/>are going to try it here 
<lb/>with the trout. What 
<lb/>is the jumping fish<reg>?</reg>
<lb/>Is it a Goby? Send 
<lb/>a line to say on what 
<lb/>particular day &amp; by 
<lb/>what train at <placeName>Kings Cross</placeName>
<lb/>you come<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p><persName>David Livingstone</persName></p>
			
